---

5. Strategic Business Recommendations  
- Clearly separate:
  - Volume reduction strategies  
  - Efficiency improvement strategies  
  - Routing optimization strategies  

---

6. AI Triage System Design (Very Important)  
- Explain how an AI triage system should work in this business  
- Include:
  - input (what data it uses)  
  - decision logic  
  - output (routing, automation, prioritization)  

---

